definitions.definition: Any of the sundry species of fish of the family Atherinidae found near Australia;
Any fish of species Atherinomorus vaigiensis and Atherinomorus lacunosus , commonly found in Australian waters.

main_definition: ( Australia ) Any of the sundry species of fish of the family Atherinidae found near Australia;
